  "prompt": "How do I sign up for Quora without Facebook?",
  "response": "You can sign up for Quora without using Facebook by following these steps:\n\n1. **Go to Quora's Website or App**: Open your web browser and visit [www.quora.com](https://www.quora.com) or download the Quora app from the App Store or Google Play Store.\n\n2. **Click on \"Sign Up\"**: On the homepage, you\u2019ll see a \"Sign Up\" button. Click on it.\n\n3. **Choose \"Sign Up with Email\"**: Instead of selecting the Facebook or Google option, choose the \"Sign Up with Email\" option.\n\n4. **Enter Your Details**: Fill in your name, email address, and create a password.\n\n5. **Verify Your Email**: After signing up, Quora will send you a verification email. Open your email inbox, find the email from Quora, and click on the verification link to confirm your account.\n\n6. **Complete Your Profile**: Once your email is verified, you can log in to Quora and complete your profile by adding a profile picture, bio, and other relevant information.\n\nBy following these steps, you can create a Quora account without using Facebook.",
